---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/ui/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - BRAVE">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About BRAVE</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Crafting premium leather goods with traditional techniques and contemporary design
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Founded on the principles of traditional craftsmanship and modern aesthetics, BRAVE creates premium leather goods that tell a story. Each piece is carefully handcrafted using time-honored techniques passed down through generations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Our commitment to quality means we source only the finest leathers and materials, ensuring that every product not only looks exceptional but stands the test of time.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            From our signature clutches to our versatile bags and accessories, each BRAVE piece is designed to be both functional and beautiful, accompanying you through life's adventures.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-square bg-gray-100">
          <img 
            src="/api/placeholder/600/600" 
            alt="Craftsman working on leather"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Process</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Selection</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We carefully select premium leathers from trusted suppliers, ensuring quality and sustainability.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Crafting</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Each piece is meticulously handcrafted using traditional techniques combined with modern precision.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Finishing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Every product undergoes rigorous quality control and receives our signature finishing touches.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Quality Guarantee</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We stand behind every product we create. Each BRAVE piece comes with our commitment to quality and craftsmanship, backed by our lifetime repair guarantee.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/collections/all"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-black text-white font-semibold hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Shop Our Collection
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>